title: Pascal Jenny
text:
Pascal Jenny (born 6 July 1978) is a former <a href="Switzerland">Swiss</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> <a href="defender%20%28football%29">defender</a>.
Career.
He currently plays for <a href="SC%20D%C3%BCdingen">SC Düdingen</a> in the First Division. Jenny previously played in the Swiss Super League for <a href="Servette%20FC">Servette FC</a>, <a href="FC%20Winterthur">FC Winterthur</a>, <a href="Yverdon-Sport">Yverdon-Sport</a>, <a href="FC%20St.%20Gallen">FC St. Gallen</a> and <a href="Neuch%C3%A2tel%20Xamax">Neuchâtel Xamax</a>.
